{"tid":718300,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一中國人在莫斯科用普通話辱罵日本妹，女球迷聽不懂全程微笑","createTime":"2018-06-26T16:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:42:01.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb6401ca2b3fcf600ba7f7ccd61c31d292e8440","tid":718300,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dqdvideofile.qnssl.com/0eRNrvAY_4697100351.mp4?sign=2b0144d05071b757ef67e4b3623f2469&amp;t=5b327603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdqdvideofile.qnssl.com%2F0eRNrvAY_4697100351.mp4%3Fsign%3D2b0144d05071b757ef67e4b3623f2469%26t%3D5b327603&d=Jxd8JfCD2g9sAqWrJKxj%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=37a9acdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://dqdvideofile.qnssl.com/0eRNrvAY_4697100351.mp4?sign=2b0144d05071b757ef67e4b3623f2469&amp;t=5b327603</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名中國球迷在俄羅斯莫斯科街頭用漢語詢問一名日本女球迷是日本人嗎，隨後對其進行辱罵侮辱。但是這名日本女球迷似乎聽不懂漢語，全程微笑面對，不過該視頻的真實性有待考證。<br />\n<br />\n此前，在日本2-1戰勝哥倫比亞的比賽之後，有一群來自哥倫比亞的男性球迷在賽后誘導一位不懂西班牙語的日本女性用西語說了&ldquo;我是一名優秀的妓女。&rdquo;，並將視頻發佈在了社交網絡上。這一行為引起了軒然大波，哥倫比亞政府為此進行了道歉。"},{"pid":"cf0ab94dc9fd53ad98905eea625a275636b3b322","tid":718300,"uid":31314,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"我地大和民族既人就係咁友善"},{"pid":"ad96a5139c814a5e73e1750378de9b25ccc9a5f2","tid":718300,"uid":11895,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"支那狗真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd823ce748b64a6ad7c57455d2285f99a9abd19","tid":718300,"uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cf0ab94dc9fd53ad98905eea625a275636b3b322","tid":718300,"uid":31314,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"我地大和民族既人就係咁友善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"好靚女，個不知所措既反應好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ea847ea9ce8b28e140f7e795fcf282762